REGION 181
CHANNEL 181
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
The cramped space beneath the wall is hardly four feet high, with a sloping
"roof" of plaster and wood. Holes in the smashed rubble threaten to turn your
ankle or grab with splinter-edged grips, tearing skin and cracking bone.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT O 2353

IFPREVERB O -1
        IFVAR POSITION ! 0
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO OTHERS %N crawls out the window.
                ECHO PLAYER You crawl out of the window.
                MOVE 2353
                AFFECT 2353
                ECHO OTHERS %N crawls out of a window in a leaning piece of wall.
        ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB STAND -1
        IFVAR HEI > 60
                IFVAR OTHERFORM ! 1
                        CLEARVERB
                        ECHO PLAYER There isn't enough room for you to stand up.
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF

ITEM 0 336
EXTEND 0 in the rubble by the window

ITEM 1 336
EXTEND 1 in the rubble to the left

ITEM 2 336
EXTEND 2 in the rubble to the right

ITEM 3 249
EXTEND 3 in a leaning section of wall
IFPREVERB GO 3
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You crawl out of the window.
        ECHO OTHERS %N crawls out the window.
        MOVE 2353
        AFFECT 2353
        ECHO OTHERS %N crawls out of a window in a leaning piece of wall.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 3
        CLEARVERB
        SHOWROOM 2353
ENDIF

ITEM 4 213 VAL2=2353
IFPREVERB GO 4
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER The rubble forms a wall, solid and interlocked wood impenetrable as far as you're concerned.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CLIMB 4
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER There's nothing to get a grip on, nowhere to climb to.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 4
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You push on the rubble above you.
        ECHO OTHERS %N pushes upwards on the rubble above you.
ENDIF

