PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
REGION 181
CHANNEL 181

*DESCRIPTION_START
Several partially ruined buildings surround this end of the main town street,
all gutted by fires and most with large holes collapsed through their walls.
The upstairs windows of the village inn look down on you, soot-stains forming
a hint of a frown above them, the doorless arch below slightly jagged, like
a mouth with only a few teeth.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=173 VAL2=2358
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
You can look right through the arch to see the open, ruined chamber within,
once the common room of the inn.
*DESCRIPTION_END

